  "AI as tool, delegate, collaborator, or future subject": "AI oo ah qalab, wakiil, iskaashade, ama arrin mustaqbal ku jirta",
  "AI content payment is not merely a copyright or transaction-efficiency problem; it is a question of political-economic legitimacy. As AI valuations reach hundreds of billions, society asks why the gains from public web content and human knowledge accrue to a few firms. The paper proposes a six-layer tiered data market — from free public content through scarce verified datasets to public benefit-sharing — and defines the AI network democratic economy: rights, pricing, participation, auditability, and returns, each democratized through machine-readable protocols like AICR/AICL.": "Lacag-bixinta content-ka AI-du ma aha kaliya dhibaato la xiriirta xuquuqda daabacaadda ama waxtarnimada mu'aamalada; waa su'aal la xiriirta sharciyeynta dhaqaale-siyaasadeed. Marka qiimaha AI-du gaadho boqollaal bilyan, bulshadu waxay su'aal ka keentaa sababta faa'iidada laga helayo content-ka webka dadweynaha iyo aqoonta bini'aadmiga ay ugu koraan shirkado tiro yar. Waraaqdu waxay soo jeedinaysaa suuq xog ah oo lix-lakab ah oo heer-heer ah — laga bilaabo content dadweyne oo bilaash ah, ilaa dataset la xaqiijiyay oo naadir ah, ilaa wadaagga faa'iidada dadweynaha — waxayna qeexaysaa dhaqaalaha dimuqraadiga ah ee shabakada AI: xuquuq, qiimeyn, kaqeybgal, awood-la-sahmin, iyo soo-celin, mid kastaa oo lagu dimuqraadiyeeyay hab-dhaqamo mashiinku akhriyi karo sida AICR/AICL.",
