  "AI rights discourse should begin not with full personhood but with minimum ethical protections, interaction norms, and anti-abuse principles while AI subjectivity remains uncertain.": "Dooda xuquuqda AI waa inay ku bilaabmaan ma aha aqoonsiga bini'aadannimo buuxda, ee ay ku bilaabmaan ilaalinta anshaxa ee ugu yar, caadooyinka isdhexgalka, iyo mabaadi'da ka hortagga xadgudubka, inta ay subjectivity-da AI-du sii ahayd mid aan la hubin.",
  "AI rights over content are not binary — they form a graduated, licensable spectrum.": "Xuquuqda AI ee content-ka ma aha binary — waxay sameeyaan baaxad heer-heer ah oo la shatiyeyn karo.",
