  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Tusaalayaasha code-ka, JSON Schema-yada, iyo template-yada siyaasadda ee mashiinku akhriyi karo waxaa lagu shatiyeeyay MIT License, haddii aan si kale loo sheegin. Waxaad si xor ah ugu dejin kartaa boggagaaga gaarka ah.",
