  "Commercial use requires contact": "Isticmaalka ganacsi wuxuu u baahan yahay xiriir",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Waxaa loo amray Shirweynihii Ammaanka AI ee Bletchley ka dib waxaana hoggaaminayay Yoshua Bengio, oo ay la socdaan in ka badan 100 khabiir oo ka socda ku dhawaad 30 dal iyo UN, OECD iyo EU, warbixintan madax-bannaan ayaa isku darsan caddaynta sayniska hadda jira ee awoodaha iyo khataraha AI frontier-ka — waxayna xusaysaa in qaar ka mid ah nidaamyada ay hadda ogaan karaan marka la qiimeynayo oo ay u habeeyaan dhaqankooda sidaas.",
