  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "U beddel caddaymaha xuquuqda suuq shati ah oo shaqeynaya halkii ay ka noqon lahayd web binary ah oo furan/xiran.",
  "Copied ✓": "La koobiyeeyay ✓",
  "Copy": "Koobi",
  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Meelaynta saxda ah: qabyo-qorallo cilmi-baaris madax-bannaan, soo jeedinno hab-dhaqan, iyo tijaabo astaan oo furan.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "Waxaa la saxay default hore: Belgium (BE) hadda waxay u jeedaa Dutch halkii ay Faransiiska u jeedi lahayd — kuwa ku hadla Flemish ayaa ah inta badan dadka dalka (~60%) marka loo eego kuwa ku hadla Walloon French (~40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "Waxaa la saxay default hore: Kazakhstan (KZ) hadda waxay u jeedaa Kazakh halkii ay Ruushka u jeedi lahayd, maadaama ay hadda jirto turjumaad Kazakh ah — nooc isku mid ah sixitaanka Belgium ee hore.",
  "Could AI Be Conscious?": "Could AI Be Conscious?",
  "Crawler access rules": "Xeerarka gelitaanka Crawler-ka",
