  "Custom tier": "Heer gaar ah",
  "Daily Nous reports on a retracted Journal of Medical Ethics submission containing multiple fabricated, AI-hallucinated references — complete with fake university affiliations and defunct email addresses — that the author reportedly left uncorrected even after being given a chance to fix proofs. The piece contrasts this with Bioethics, whose automated reference-checking would have caught the problem, and argues the real bottleneck isn't detection technology (one commenter's script flagged the fake citations in under a minute) but unpaid reviewer labor and publishing incentives that reward throughput over scrutiny.": "Daily Nous waxay ka warbixisaa gudbin laga soo celiyay oo ka mid ahaa Journal of Medical Ethics oo ay ku jiraan dhowr tixraac oo la been-abuurtay, oo uu AI-du soo hallucinate garay — oo ay la socdaan xiriirro jaamacadeed been ah iyo cinwaano email aan shaqaynayn — kuwaas oo qoraagu si la sheegay uga sii daayay iyadoon la saxin xitaa markii isaga la siiyay fursad uu ku saxo caddaymaha. Sheekadu waxay barbardhigaysaa tan Bioethics, oo automated-ka hubinta tixraacyadeeda ay dhici lahayd inay qabato dhibaatada, waxayna ku doodaysa in caqabadda dhabta ahi aysan ahayn tignoolajiyada ogaanshaha (script koodh ka mid ah faallooyinka ayaa calaamadeeyay tixraacyada beenta ah wax ka yar hal daqiiqo) balse ay tahay shaqada dib-u-eegayaasha aan la bixin iyo dhiirigelinta daabacaadda ee abaal-marisa tirada halkii ay abaal-marin lahayd baaritaanka.",
  "Data free-riding vs. trillion-dollar AI valuations": "Xogta oo lala socdaalo bilaash iyo qiimaha AI ee trilyan-dollarka ah",
  "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI": "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI",
  "Demis Hassabis proposed a FINRA-style regulator for frontier model releases: labs would submit models for review up to 30 days before deployment, voluntary at first, with a path toward mandatory compliance in the US market.": "Demis Hassabis ayaa soo jeediyay hay'ad xakamayn oo qaabka FINRA u eg oo loogu talagalay sii-daynta model-yada frontier-ka ah: sheybaarrada waxay u gudbin lahaayeen model-yada dib-u-eegis ilaa 30 maalmood ka hor deployment-ka, marka hore iskaa-wax-u-qabso ahaan, iyagoo leh waddo u socota lahoggaansanaan qasab ah oo ku jirta suuqa Mareykanka.",
  "Denied": "La diiday",
  "Deployable policy starter template": "Template bilow siyaasadeed oo la dejin karo",
  "Deployable policy starter template at /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — a minimal static site with the full machine-readable layer, ready for Cloudflare Pages or any static host.": "Template bilow siyaasadeed oo la dejin karo, oo ku yaal /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — bog static ah oo ugu yar oo leh lakabka mashiinku akhriyi karo oo dhammaystiran, oo diyaar u ah Cloudflare Pages ama martigelin static kasta.",
  "Deploying machine-readable policies on your site": "Ku dejinta siyaasadaha mashiinku akhriyi karo boggaaga",
  "Disclaimer": "Digniin",
  "Distinct from human UI, SEO, or plain APIs, the AI Ingestion & Capability Layer gives websites a machine-facing architecture: a Manifest Layer (entry points like /llms.txt and /ai/manifest.json), a Corpus Layer (machine-readable knowledge), a Capability Layer (agent-callable tools), and a Governance Layer (provenance, licensing, versioning). Static-first, upgradeable toward APIs and MCP. Note: in this paper AICL names the ingestion architecture; on this site's protocol pages AICL refers to the AI Content Licensing Layer.": "Iyadoo ka duwan UI-ga bini'aadamka, SEO-ga, ama API-yada caadiga ah, AI Ingestion & Capability Layer wuxuu website-yada siiyaa naqshad u jeeda mashiinka: Manifest Layer (bar-gelitaanno sida /llms.txt iyo /ai/manifest.json), Corpus Layer (aqoon mashiinku akhriyi karo), Capability Layer (aaladaha agent-adu wici karaan), iyo Governance Layer (asalka, shatiyeynta, noocyada). Static-ka ayaa mudnaanta koowaad leh, waxaana loo kordhin karaa API-yo iyo MCP. Fiiro gaar ah: waraaqdan AICL wuxuu u yaqaan naqshadda ingestion-ka; bogagga hab-dhaqan ee boggan AICL wuxuu ka dhigan yahay AI Content Licensing Layer.",
  "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm": "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm",
  "Docs": "Dukumentiyada",
