  "Document library": "Maktabadda Dukumentiyada",
  "Does AI have rights — and which framings are even coherent?": "AI ma leeyahay xuquuq — iyo kee ka mid ah qaabaynta ayaa xitaa isku xigxiga?",
  "Download": "Soo deji",
  "Draft status": "Xaaladda Qabyo-qoraalka",
  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Tijaabo waxbarasho: HMAC-SHA256 oo leh sir la wadaago, oo muujinaysa token-yo shati ah oo ku xiran codsiga, waqti dhammaan kara, oo la xaqiijin karo. Token-yada wax-soo-saarka waa inay noqdaan kuwo asymmetric loo saxeexay, iyadoo furaha dadweynaha ee daabacaha laga heli karo /.well-known/.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Siddeed entry oo kale oo /topics ah, markan waxaa cilmi-baaray agent AI ah halkii lagu ururin lahaa gacanta — isla xeer hore: il kasta waa la soo qaatay oo si toos ah loo xaqiijiyay, soo-koobidaha waa qoraal asal ah, ka hor inta aan wax lagu darin. Wadar ahaan 14 entry.",
  "Email": "Iimayl",
