  "verbatim_memory — whether exact reproduction is permitted": "verbatim_memory — in soo-saaridda saxda ah la oggol yahay iyo in kale",
  "versioned, citable, traceable": "nooc-lahaansho leh, la tixraaci karo, la raadraaci karo",
  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "\"AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer\" hadda waxaa lagu daabacay Ingiriisi sida nooca rasmiga ah; qoraalka asalka ah ee Shiineeska ayaa sii jira, labada noocna way isku xidhan yihiin.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "\"Protocolized Openness\" waxaa loo xaqiijiyay inay tahay waraaq luqad Ingiriisi ah (oo leh qaybo Shiine ah oo isla socda) — turjumaad gooni ah lama qorsheynin.",
  "↑ live machine-readable policy of this site": "↑ siyaasadda mashiinku akhriyi karo ee boggan, toos ah",
